Jess Hilarious Is Killin It on Wild N Out! (Ya Titties Don't Have To Be Big ) w/ D.C. Lous and Chico See 85 South Live in Atlanta or D.C.! http://www.85southshow.com/live On this episode - recorded late at night in New York City - the crew breaks out into a new hit song "Ya Titties Don't Have To Be Real" followed by a Mr. Biggs (Chico Bean) and R Kelly (D.C. Young Fly) impromptu impersonation song and then Jess Hilarious talks about the time she met Martin Lawrence. The crew also share tragic car accident horror stories and then catch up on the new season of Wild N Out and what it takes to be a new cast member on the show. Jess Hilarious also addresses critics who had negative things to say about her naked photo shoot with her son.
